<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="heavily-adv">heavily <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hevɪli/    美 /'hevɪli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重重地；沉重地；严重地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father was <strong>drinking / smoking heavily</strong> by then.
那时我父亲喝酒喝得厉害/抽烟抽得厉害。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It was dark and raining heavily.
天很黑，雨下得很大。</p><footer>2011 浙江</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Mr Smith used to smoke <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (heavy) but he has given it up.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. heavily  </p></div>